0.3.1-1
Sun, 03 Dec 2006 19:05:56 -0300
* disabled mail report. has to be rethought.
* warn for repos asked via command line which doesn't have a definition in the config file.
* better error handling.
* correct dependencies and suggestions.
* more correct consistency implementation.
* support for undefined fields in repo definitions.
* more drivers: Cpan, Mozilla, OpenOfficeOrg.
* does not depend on python-apt anymore.
* new driver API, more suitable for different repo structures.
* lots of bug fixes.
-- Marcos Dione <mdione@grulic.org.ar>
0.2.4a-1
Fri, 06 Jan 2006 08:46:51 -0300
* fixed bug in the Urpmi driver that prevented to download a Mandrake distro.
* more example repos defined with the new format.
-- Marcos Dione <mdione@grulic.org.ar>
0.2.4-1
Wed, 04 Jan 2006 14:43:06 -0300
* Full support for Urpmi repositories.
* Support for several archs and downloading of Release files for Debian repositories.
* More verbose help. 
* Much better summary email with total MiB per module. 
* More examples in the config file.
* Lots of docs, both in the project site and the distribution package. 
* Better info when not in verbose or debug mode.
* Processes the rest of the repo even if there was some problem with one module.
* Several bugfixes.
-- Marcos Dione <mdione@grulic.org.ar>
